Maytag,

Sounds like your transfer is just fine. When you put the transfer in neutral
your doing just that, its in neutral just like your regulat trans would be. no
power boing through it. Reason for the grinding sounds in the automatic is that
it's running wide open when yur trying to put it in neutral, your trying to do
the same thing as if you were going down the road and decided to put the trans in
park at 50 MPH.

Hope you learn what a 4 x 4 is really like before you wreck it.

Dick Nixon @
Nixon's Truck Parts, Inc.

